# radlibsapp-service-account.json

# This is your Firebase Admin SDK service account key
# NEVER commit this file to Git - it provides full admin access to your Firebase project

# To get this file:
# 1. Go to: https://console.firebase.google.com/project/radlibsapp/settings/serviceaccounts
# 2. Click "Generate new private key"
# 3. Save the downloaded file as "radlibsapp-service-account.json" in this directory

# Security Notes:
# - This file grants admin access to your Firebase database
# - Keep it secure and never share publicly
# - Regenerate if compromised
# - Each admin should have their own service account for audit trails
